_sText:
Description:
Fairly small combine-environment map with ~16 spawn points per team. Designed for deathmatch, but can be played with rounds.

Features:
2d skybox
.nav file
multi-floor design

Instillation:
Extract the .bsp and .nav to your \cstrike\maps folder and play

Notes:
- If you like the map leave feedback and a rating on what you liked, didn't like, or what you think could be improved upon. If you didn't like it, feel free to leave suggestions and what made it an un-pleasurable experience

Updates:
- Doubled sun brightness
- Added ~15 more lights and light_spots for more visibility
- Couple texture glitch fixes
